{"tid":1037612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少女感太強了！朴信惠溫婉長髮變元氣波波頭，看完都想剪","createTime":"2019-02-26T05:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T23:06:09.000Z","uid":9573,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9b69ae3303bec87f548fbe5c94b6fc1c67c919","tid":1037612,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"提起朴信惠，一定會想到她那頭濃密黑亮的大波浪卷髮，真的是女人味十足。 然而新年要有新氣象，朴信惠就以短髮登上了熱搜榜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_969605b19a161630118af9c08dc83ae6/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708676.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_969605b19a161630118af9c08dc83ae6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708676.png&h=43661c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_bf984e93f60cbcf945b202214eb993a4/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708678.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_bf984e93f60cbcf945b202214eb993a4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708678.png&h=6af7dcda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾經是長髮的朴信惠自帶女神氣場，婉約嫵媚，超具女人味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_218b726a41072eab3529fcd444fb5daa/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708680.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_218b726a41072eab3529fcd444fb5daa%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708680.png&h=f018e3d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_468cf67e7d2b4050ccba6d15e3cb11da/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708686.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_468cf67e7d2b4050ccba6d15e3cb11da%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708686.png&h=d0354d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_51760451bd6e7bf232e9604564b2c798/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708682.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_51760451bd6e7bf232e9604564b2c798%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708682.png&h=070b1d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而朴信惠今年則挑戰了「耳下三公分」短髮，讓五官更顯立體精緻。 齊下巴的長度清爽又可愛，空氣劉海減少了厚重感，少女味十足。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e40093e76a3debed6cf28332d80189cd/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708688.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e40093e76a3debed6cf28332d80189cd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708688.png&h=607e199f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a0491a2c0e779d394235b0f369835199/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708690.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a0491a2c0e779d394235b0f369835199%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708690.png&h=66b9c2c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用卷髮棒卷過之後是不是立刻多了幾分成熟感覺呢？ 短髮也有很多造型可嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_823cc5e16b1c9635bbc6cb0ff56b8c0d/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708695.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_823cc5e16b1c9635bbc6cb0ff56b8c0d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708695.png&h=b2ade43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_10db36f625369a4fab19374bd6c4df94/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708698.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_10db36f625369a4fab19374bd6c4df94%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708698.png&h=e78f3269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_949c8c345f48ec39806823b6cabd11b7/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708699.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_949c8c345f48ec39806823b6cabd11b7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708699.png&h=d5e75d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fe7bfa91a4e67af87263f6c4c048644e/static.koreastardaily.com/2019-02-22/114210-708685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fe7bfa91a4e67af87263f6c4c048644e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2019-02-22%2F114210-708685.jpg&h=f8583e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eastweek.com.hk/resources/60808/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eastweek.com.hk%2Fresources%2F60808%2F2.jpg&h=cd23d472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據說，朴信惠是因為新電影的角色所以換了短髮造型，鏡頭中的朴信惠大方展示自己的短髮，還擺出各種可愛表情。朴信惠的新髮型得到了無數好評，不少網友表示想剪個同款短髮。"},{"pid":"65f64dbb3d582ab58f04ed970096301ddc09cacc","tid":1037612,"uid":209029,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"最尾又做咩"},{"pid":"bc472b513eaae1f8b40614464d0b5b559aeb687d","tid":1037612,"uid":43061,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"屌打身痕結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e833619bd72f32a9a36f029920eb1e6fceb16d3a","tid":1037612,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8d/Art-Jigglypuff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8d%2FArt-Jigglypuff.png&h=cd713ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86570ad801acc2314304b87b33554d9ac537427","tid":1037612,"uid":209029,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"短髮都好正，不過以前長髮似女神多d"},{"